Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナに誓う}—Episode 018—\NA promise to Shellenina
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:00.90,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{美しい海。}What a beautiful ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:03.74,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{美しい山。}Such pretty mountains, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:06.81,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{この国は小さいけど、美しい国だわ。}It's such a small country, but it is so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:11.80,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{それにしても、昨日のあの試合を許せない。}However, I can't get over the yesterday's match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:16.36,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{鮎原。なぜか私このままあなたと分かれてしまいたくない。}Ayuhara, for some reason I don't want to part our ways like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:20.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしは鮎原こずえです。}I'm Ayuhara Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.44,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,{私はソ連ジュニアチームのコーチ、ルドルフです。}I'm Soviet Union junior team's coach, Rudolph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:31.35,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,{実はキャプテンのシェレーニナは是非あなたと二人きりでお話をしたいと。}As a matter of fact, captain Shellenina wants to speak to you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:34.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？シェレーニナ様今どこに？}Oh? Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:36.16,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,{千本松原で。}She's waiting for you in the pine grove.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{千本松原？}In the pine grove?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:49.47,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{バレーを捨てたあたしに、今更一体何よ。}What does she want from me now that I quit volleyball?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:52.50,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あなたと話し合うことなど何もないはずなのに。}We don't have anything to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.09,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{でもあなたのXXX。}And yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:56.17,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{なぜかあたしをあなたに引かれるの？}Why did you call me over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:02:59.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナさん。}Shellenina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:03.86,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:06.29,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{わざわざ呼び出してごめんなさいね。}I'm sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.72,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{どうしてもこのままは分かれたくなかった。}I wanted to talk to you one more time by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:16.56,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{皆昨日の試合のせいです。}It's about the yesterday's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:17.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{勝った試合未だ不満があるの？}Are you not satisfied with your victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.45,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{そう。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:22.21,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{不満があるのです。}I'm not satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.66,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{それは特にあなたに。}Particularly about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:27.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{私に？あたしが何をしたっと言うの？}About me? What did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:29.39,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{日本一富士見学園のプレー。}The Japan's best Fujimi Academy's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.26,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{勝敗ぬきで良い試合できる。}It doesn't have to do with winning or losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.95,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{あたし信じていました。}I believed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:36.32,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{しかし、あなた方真剣でなかった。}But you weren't serious at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.72,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{初めてから試合を捨てていた。}You forfeited the game right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:39.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{誤解だわ。}You got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは一所懸命にだったわ。}We did our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{本当よ。}We really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.02,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{でもあなたたちはXXX。}But you were too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{実力の差です。}It's the difference in our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{どうしようもない実力の差で乾杯したんです。}We lost because of the skill difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.95,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{実力？}Skill?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.10,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{とんでもない。}Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.87,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{あなた実力も半分を出してなかった。}You haven't shown half of your skill to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:21.51,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{全日本の決勝戦の時に素晴らしいゲームを見せてくれたのに。}You've shown us such a splendid game during the All-Japan championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:24.15,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{あれは実力だ何て、私は信じません。}I can't believe that was the full extent of your skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.00,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.77,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{どうか正直に答えてください。}Please, be honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:34.13,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{昨日あなたはコートで何を考えていたのですか？}What were you thinking about in the court yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:37.56,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{私たちの試合に勝つことだけを考えていましたか？}Was it only about winning with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.00,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{恐ろしい。}She's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.08,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{この人は皆見抜いている。}This person can see right through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.87,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしの心のXXXも。}She sensed it flawlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:51.18,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{試合の時私はバレーよりも体育館や首位刺々しいしてに心を奪われていた。}Rather than focusing on the game, I was thinking about the gym construction and the club's politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.63,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:57.28,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{あなた心の底に何か大きいな悩みがあるですね。}There is something big that troubles you, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:01.01,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{そして昨日の試合には別の目的が混じってましたね。}The yesterday's game collided with some other goal, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{すみません。その通りです。}I'm sorry. You're completely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{でもどうしてそれを？}But how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.81,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{同じバレーをやっているもの同士。}We both play the same volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:09.60,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{一つのボールを打ち合うのです。}We hit the same ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.21,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{分からないはず無い。}Of course we understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:14.53,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{でも、あなたの答えを聞いた安心した。}I'm relieved after hearing your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.11,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{私は思った通り。}It's just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:19.21,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{昨日のあなたは本当のあなたじゃなかったのです。}You just weren't yourselves yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしは…}But I…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.18,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:27.26,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{このXXX何も話し手も始まらない。}It doesn't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{でも皆終わりだわ。}It's all over anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.79,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしはもうバレーを捨てたんだもん。}I quit volleyball after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.21,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:38.23,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{今度試合する時本当のあなたを打付けれますね。}You'll be serious the next time we play, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.91,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{それを期待します。}I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.83,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{鮎原、あなたはきっと、きっと…}Ayuhara, I'm positive…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:48.97,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{私の一番恐ろしいライバルに成ると思います。}…that you will become my best rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:52.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ライバル？そんなこと勝手に決めてもらっては困るだわ。}Your rival? Please don't suddenly decide such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.04,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{必ずあなたはライバルに成る。}You'll surely become my rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.36,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{もしそうでなかったら…}If you don't…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうでなかったら？}If I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:06:01.06,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{昨日の試合のこと死ぬまで許しません。}I won't forgive you that game until the end of my days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:08.52,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{私の気持ち分かってもらいましたね？}Do you understand my feelings now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え。よく分かりました。}Yes. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.92,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{有難う。}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:16.01,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{では、あしたの日曜日東京へ来てください。}Please come to Tokyo tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:18.69,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{日本での最後の試合見てほしい。}I want to show you our last game in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{でも、どうして？}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.80,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{見てもらえば分かります。}You'll understand when you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.84,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{じゃ、あした。東京で。}See you tomorrow in Tokyo.
