Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.06,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:09.38,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,{相手は男子高校チームなので、驚いてますね？}Our opponents is a high school boys team. Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:13.87,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,{でもその理由はもうじきあなたにもはっきり分かるはず。}The reason should make itself evident pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:18.48,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{相手は高校男子で、然も巻頭のベストエイトに選ばれた北側高校。}The opponent is Kitakawa, a high school boys team which was chosen as the best eight in Kantou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.53,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{今までよりXXX当然んだわ。}They're better than the prior opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{でも別に何も変わってXないじゃないわ。}But I don't see anything out of ordinary so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:26.50,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{これはシェレーニナはあたしに見せようとしてる試合なのかしら？}Is this the game Shellenina wanted to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:29.47,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{ソ連女子・北川高校男子}Soviet Union ・ Kitakawa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.77,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{何も起これなかった。}Nothing happened at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:34.59,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それとこの第二セットに何が起こるかしら?}Or is it supposed to happen in the second set?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:40.94,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{ソ連女子・北川高校男子}Soviet Union ・ Kitakawa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:41.56,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{タイム。}Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.52,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{ピンチサーバー、ボルチンスカヤ。}Pinch server, Borchinskaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.40,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{ボルチンスカヤ。練習通りにやるのよ。}Borchinskaya, let's do this just like we practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:08.98,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,{あの選手はまだ(X・起立)が不足のため公式試合には出したことがありません。}That player wasn't put in any official match yet because of her inability to stand upright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:12.32,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,{今シェレーニナは特訓中の秘密兵器なのです。}She's under Shellenina's strict training as her secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それと？}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.82,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{思い切ってやりなさい。}Take your pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.74,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{サーブでは何も起こらない。}Nothing happened during the serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:28.46,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{とうすれば、ボルチンスカヤはアタック攻撃に回った特に。}Does it mean Borchinskaya's power manifests in the attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:31.44,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{ソ連女子・北川高校男子}Soviet Union ・ Kitakawa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.30,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{いよいよボルチンスカヤはXXX回って来た。}Finally Borchinskaya's on the attacking position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:39.87,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ここだわ、きっと。}That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.86,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{可笑しい。こんなはずはないわ。}Strange. It was pretty ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:09:01.36,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナはあたしに何を見せるつもりなんだろう？}What did Shellenina exactly want to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:04.73,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。拍子抜けなさってますね。}Ayuhara-san. You seem disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.56,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,{ヒントを言いましょう。}Let me give you a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:10.86,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナはセンターに入った時に気をつけてください。}Pay attention when Shellenina gets in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.30,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{センターに？}In the center?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.96,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{チャンスボール。}Chance ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.25,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{お！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.30,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—どうした？\N—おい、どうした？}– What's wrong?\N– Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.30,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—どうした？\N—X、どうした？}– Are you hurt?\N– You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.87,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{手、手が。}My hand. My hand…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.41,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{大丈夫か？}Should I call for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:52.17,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あの攻撃、すごい破壊力。}What a destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナ、あなたは恐ろしい人だわ。}Shellenina, you are a scary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:59.04,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あ、悪夢だは、きっと。こんな試合は言い訳が無い。}It must be a nightmare. There was no defending this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:01.73,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:06.05,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{どうでした？この試合をあなたに見てもらった理由が分かりましたか？}How was it? Do you now see why I wanted to show you our game?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:13.34,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{あなたに早く日本人のアタッカーの情熱のファイト取り戻してほしいのです。}I want to bring the Japanese attacker's passion back to you as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:18.72,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{このボルチンスカヤ右足不自由んです。}Borchinskaya can't use her right leg very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.72,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{小さい時XXしました。}She hurt it when she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.35,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{バレーにはジャンプ一番必要なのに。}In volleyball, one needs a good jump the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.95,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{そのジャンプ力は普通の人の半分もない。}But she can't jump half as high as an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:31.44,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{でもボルチンスカヤどしてもバレーがやりたい。}However, Borchinskaya wants to play no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:36.85,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{それで彼女とわたくし二人で考え出したのは十字トスです。}That is why she and I thought of our own technique, which we call a "cross toss".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{十字トス？}A cross toss…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:40.16,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{そう。十字トス。}Yep. A cross toss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:44.24,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{ボルチンスカヤのアタック低いXXと打ちます。}Borchinskaya hits the ball low.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:48.71,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{だから、変化球で破壊力をつけなければならない。}That's why I need to make it powerful with a curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:53.03,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{そこで私センターに入ってトスボールに回転を当たれ…}When I'm in the center, I give rotation to the ball and pass it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:57.94,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{ボルチンスカヤはそれをさらに強い力で変化させます。}Borchinskaya accepts it and hits it with even stronger force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.64,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。あたしは国へ変える。}Ayuhara-san. I'm going back to Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:04.35,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{十字トスとボルチンスカヤもさらに、さらに鍛えます。}I'll train cross toss and Borchinskaya even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.76,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{そしてあなたの挑戦を待っています。}And I will wait for your letter of challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.56,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え。いいわ、シェレーニナさん。}Very well, Shellenina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.03,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{今度のお会いする時…}When we meet again…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.46,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{必ずコートで。さようなら。}…let's meet in the court. Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{さようなら。}Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:26.00,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{あたしは十字トスとボルチンスカヤを更に鍛えます。}"I'll train cross toss and Borchinskaya even more."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:29.01,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そしてあなたの挑戦を待っています。}"And I will wait for your letter of challenge."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.23,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナ。}Shellenina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.54,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{おかげで一つをはっきりしたわ。}Thanks to you, I understood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.92,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしはバレー無では生きていけないのよ。}I can't go on without volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:39.08,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしはバレー部に帰る。バレー部へ。}I will return to volleyball… to our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.60,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.29,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:43.92,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{行くわよ。}Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:44.64,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,{はい。}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:45.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:46.80,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:47.66,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:49.20,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{もういっぽん。}Once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.44,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{よいっしょう。}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:52.88,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{あら？鮎原さんはバレーをやるXXX。}I thought Ayuhara-san quit volleyball?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.09,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{嘘だったのかしら。}I guess it was a false rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.52,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{嘘も決まってるわ。}Of course it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:59.30,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{鮎原とXXバレーXX考えられないもう。}I can't think of Ayuhara Kozue without thinking of volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:00.16,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{もういっぽん。}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:00.74,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{おう！}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:01.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい。}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:03.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ごめんなさい。}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:08.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.02,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{君にちょっと話がある。}I want to talk to you for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.42,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{神社の境内へ待っているよ。}I'll be waiting for you on the shrine's premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{お？}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{努くん。}Tsutomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:22.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ね、話して何よ。あたし今XX練習したいの。}What did you want to talk about? I need to go back to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:23.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ね？}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.73,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{え？}Ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:27.00,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{君はバレー部を止めたんじゃなかったのか？}I thought you quit the volleyball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:30.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そんなこと努くんに何も関係ないことでしょう？}It has nothing to do with you, Tsutomu-kun, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{誰がどう思うとあたしはバレーをやるのよ。}I'll play volleyball no matter what people think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:36.48,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{フン。そしてもう一度優勝旗を振り回そうって言うのか？}Hmph. Then you'll wave the championship pennant again, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:40.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{お生憎様。あたしはそんなちっちゃなことを狙ってないわ。}Too bad, I don't have such a small goal anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしの敵はソ連のシェレーニナよ。}Shellenina of the Soviet Union is my rival now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.04,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナ？}Shellenina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:47.04,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{こずえくん。君はやっぱり分かってないんだな。}Kozue-kun, you still don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{なんとでもおっしゃい。}Say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナさんと約束したのよ。}I made a promise to Shellenina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:53.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{今度会う時にかならず勝つって。}When we meet again, we'll win for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.12,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{勝つ？}Win?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.11,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{立派だよ。}How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.77,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{バレーの目的はただ勝つことにXXXね。}I see that the volleyball club's goal is still just to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{もう止めて。}Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:03.34,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{努くん何かにはあたしの今の気持ちが分かってたまるもんですか。}Tsutomu-kun, you don't understand me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.55,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{こずえくん。}Kozue-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{努くん。}Tsutomu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:09.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あなたはあたしがバレー部を止めればいいと思ってるのね。}You'd be overjoyed if I quit volleyball, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:10.07,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{何だって？}Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:11.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{分かってるわよ。}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:16.96,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしがバレー部を止めれば、そうすれば、もうバレー部専用の体育館を建てるなんて言わないと思って。}If I quit our club, if I did that… you wouldn't have to oppose the building of the new gym anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.12,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{バカ！}Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え。どうせあたしはバカよ。}Yeah, I'm an idiot after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:21.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{放っといて。}Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.75,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{こずえくん。}Kozue-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{何よ、放してよ。}What now? Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:26.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あなたに何か関係ないわ。}What I do is none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:27.89,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{何だと？}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.93,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{君は自分が…}You… you're only…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:38.74,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{待てよ、一ノ瀬。}Hey, Ichinose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:42.38,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{せっかくはりきってる鮎原くんをケチを付けるな。}Don't you pick on Ayuhara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.96,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{スポーツ(XX・漫画)試合に勝って、何が悪いんだよ。}What's wrong about winning in sports?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:48.92,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{第一スポーツもやったこともない貴様何かに…}What the hell do you know, nerd?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.51,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{…鮎原くんをせめるしかくがあると思ってるのか？}Think you're in any position to preach to Ayuhara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:54.40,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{三田村、僕は責めるんじゃない。}Mitamura, I'm not preaching to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{僕はこずえのこと心配してるんだ。}I'm only worried about Kozue-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.48,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{チェ。このやろ。}Tch, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.79,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{やろ。}Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.00,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{やったな。}Now you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:06.72,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{えい。卑怯だ。この。}Fight back, you coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:07.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{止めて。}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:08.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{止めてよ。}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{止めてったら、二人共。}I'm telling you to stop, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:14.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{喧嘩するなら、あたしの見てない所でやってちょうだい。}If you need to fight, take it to where I can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{迷惑だわ。}Your fight is an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:19.23,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしのこと心配してくれるのありがたいけど。}Thanks for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あなたたち何も、何も分かっちゃいないのよ。}But you don't understand anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:24.03,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{そんな。ばかな。}No way. I get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{いいえ。そうよ。}Nope, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:28.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あなたたちがどう思うと、あたしはやりたいことをやるわ。}I'll be doing what I want to whatever any of you say to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:34.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{だからもう二度とあたしのこと口出ししないで。}Don't interfere with my life ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{さようなら。}Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:55.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:21.50,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{君たちは何のためにバレーをやっているんだ?}"What are you playing volleyball for?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.50,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{鮎原。答えろ。}"Ayuhara. You first."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:32.68,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{バレーのも目的はただ勝つことなのさ。}"The volleyball club's goal is still just to win."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.76,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうよ。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:36.73,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナにはあたしは勝つ。}I'll win with Shellenina.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:38.46,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{絶対に勝つわ。}I'll win without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.29,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{例え誰が何と言おうと。}No matter what everyone says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.99,Alternative,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{こずえ。}Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.58,Alternative,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{お前は自分の方針から目を背け落としている。}It seems you're unable to focus on your true goals now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.34,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{こずえ。}Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あら、おかえりなさい、パパ。}Oh, welcome back, papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.26,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{お前に見せたい物がある。}I want to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:53.88,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{パパの部屋へお出で。}Come to papa's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.82,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{見せたい物？}What does he want to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？なに、これ？}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.02,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{ドイツ語の辞書だ。}It's a German dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ドイツ語の？}German?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:08.87,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—あら、中身がないわ。\N—破って捨てたさ。}– But it has no contents?\N– I torn the pages and threw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{破って？}Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.88,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{パパが学生のころの話だが。}It's a story from papa's student times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:17.09,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{この辞書に乗っている単語全部覚えてやろうと決心したんだよ。}I had a resolution to remember all of the words inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:23.39,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{所が五百ページもある単語を覚えると言うとはそれは並大抵のことじゃない。}To remember five hundred pages worth of words is no small feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.46,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{そこで色々と考えたXX…}I focused really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.09,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{一ページ覚えるの時に、そのページを破り捨てたんだ。}When I've remembered one page, I torn it and threw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:36.65,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{そして、最後の一ページを破り捨てた時は…}When I torn the last page…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.97,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{世界を征服したなような気分だったよ。}…I felt like I've conquered the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:45.23,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{それ以来このページのない辞書はパパの宝に成ったんだよ。}This dictionary without pages is papa's treasure ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.29,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{分かるか、こずえ？}See what I'm getting at, Kozue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:51.19,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{人のできないことに、全力をかけて、ぶつかっていく。}It's about courage to confront things viewed as impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.02,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{それが青春と言うものじゃないか？}Isn't that what youth is all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:58.83,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{例えそれは失敗に終わっても目的に向かって最後まで我武者羅にぶつかっていく。}Even if it ends with failure, you should approach your goals with full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:01.83,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{大切なのは前向きな姿勢じゃないかと思ったからね。}What matters the most is the positive attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.20,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{どうした、こずえ？}What's wrong, Kozue?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:08.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{パパ、あたしは分かってるのような気がするの。}Papa, I think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:14.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{先生、あたしは分かったんです。}Professor, I understand it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:15.52,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{ん？}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:20.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{先生のおっしゃった、何のためにバレーをやるかが分かったんです。}I know the answer to your question as to what we're playing volleyball for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{聞こう。言ってご覧。}Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:27.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしたち優勝することばかり考えて感じが大事なことを忘れていたようです。}I feel we forgot something important in the craze about winning the championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:35.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{口ではうまく言えませんけど、優勝のそのまた先にある何か私たちは目指さなければいけなかったんです。}I can't say it very well, but… I think we should have been aiming for something else as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:40.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そのために厳しい練習もうし、人間の限界まで挑戦する。}That goal is the reason we practice so hard. We challenge the limits of human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.38,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{そうだ。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:44.55,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{そして、その動力の代償は優勝なんだ。}And victories are the compensation for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:49.24,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{人は優勝、優勝とさないけど勝った瞬間それはもう過去の栄光にしか過ぎない。}People keep saying "victory, victory". But the moment you win, it becomes the glory of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:53.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{大切なことは狙いに向かってぶつかっていく心構え。}What's important is to aim for one's goals and maintain a positive attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.73,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうでしょう、先生？}Isn't that right, professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:56.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{その通り。}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:57.72,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{しかし、鮎原。}But Ayuhara…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:01.45,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{それほどのこと、君一人で考えついたと思えないが。}I don't think you came to this realization by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え。実は、父に。}My dad helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.56,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{お？良いお父さんだ。}Hoo? You've got a good father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.06,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{君は幸せものだぞ。}You're one happy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい。}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.86,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そしてもう一人シェレーニナ。}Then there's you, Shellenina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナ、今私には分かる。}Shellenina, I understand it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:14.81,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あなたの力強い思いやりが。}Your kindhearted strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:20.27,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしはもう見えない。この少し(XXX・奥深い)バレーの世界からもう逃げることはできない。}I can't escape. Now I see that I cannot escape from the volleyball world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:23.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:24.94,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:27.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:29.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:31.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.60,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{あ、すごい。}Whoa, awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.64,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{今日の親分何だXXX見たい。}Our chief looks different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:39.40,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{それはそうよ。XXX近づいたんですもの。}Of course she does. She looks happy for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:41.35,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{当然よ。ね、こずえ？}It's only natural. Right, Kozue?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え。でも皆誤解しないでね。}Yeah. But make no mistake, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:48.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{もうあたしは秋の全国大会でただ優勝すれば良いとだけと思ってるわけじゃないんだから。}I no longer think about just the winning of the autumn's All-Japan championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{目的が別にあるの。}I have another objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:53.79,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{あら？あたしは優勝第一目的やってるつもりだけど？}Oh? I intended to make winning this championship my primary objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:56.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ただ優勝、優勝って、あまり優勝に拘れと。}Winning this, winning that. It will get us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:59.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{大きな落とし穴に落ちるといけないと思って。}Such a point of view will only land us in a big pitfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.06,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{落とし穴？}A pitfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:01.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そう。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:07.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{どん詰まりの前には必ず落とし穴があるけど、 私たちのバレー部は突き当たりがないのよ。}There are always pitfalls before the end of the road. But for our club, the end is nowhere to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.19,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{ね、ナカ。}Hey, Naka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:12.19,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{あたしたちのこの気持ちが 他の部の人たちにも 分かってもらえるといいんだけどね。}I hope that people from other clubs can understand our feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.68,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{うん。そうすればさ…}Yep. If they do…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:18.19,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{…バレー部専用体育館の建設に 繁体する人もいなくなるのにね。}…there will be no one that opposes the construction of a gym for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それはもう諦めましょう。}Let's give up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:24.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ソ連チームに負けた以上、あたしたち そんなXXX出す資格はないですもの。}We're in no place to ask for it after losing to the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:28.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)}{クラブ機会\N会議中}Club meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:36.08,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{では前回からの持ち越し 時代である バレー部専用の体育館建設について 会議を開きます。}We will now resume the debate about the construction of a gym for the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:38.48,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{意見がある方はどうぞ。}If you have an opinion, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.44,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{はい。}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{その前にあたしから一言言わせてください。}Before that, please hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:43.44,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:47.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{体育館の問題を取り下げてください。}Please withdraw the construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.14,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{え？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:51.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしたち、野沢さんと一ノ瀬さん言われた通り…}Just like Nozawa-san and Ichinose-san said…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{…今後は外で練習することにします。}…we will practice outdoors from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それだけです。}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.53,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{え？一体どう言うことなの？}– Huh?\N– What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.98,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—飽きれたね。\N—そんなにXXくせにね。}– How surprising.\N– I never expected that from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:04.82,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{ちょっと。鮎原くんに質問があります。}Excuse me. I have a question to Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:05.83,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{どうぞ。}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.47,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{なぜそんなに急にこの問題を取り下げちゃったんですか？}Why are you suddenly withdrawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:13.27,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{体育館の建設には賛成もあるってこと忘れずに。}Do not forget that some of us have agreed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:18.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{でもあたしたちはバレーさえ出来れば どこでもよかったんです。}But we can play volleyball pretty much anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:22.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{立派な練習XXXあたしたちの間違いでした。}We were wrong to demand such a privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:26.76,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{議長。僕も体育館の建設に賛成です。}Chairman. I agree to the construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.76,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—え？\N—変ね。}– Eh?\N– That was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.76,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{あんた、裏切り者よ。}How could you betray us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:34.70,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{XXX。一ノ瀬くん続けてください。}Settle down. Ichinose-kun, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:37.05,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{この間まで僕は反対でした。}Up until now I opposed this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.47,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{専用の体育館がなければ、練習できないとか。}"We can't practice without a gym of our own."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.69,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{全国大会に優勝したんだから、XXXとか。}"We won an All-Japan tournament, so give us money."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:44.90,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{そう言うバレー部のようきょうだったら、 今でも僕は反対です。}If they continued to hold onto this attitude, I'd still oppose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:46.70,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{でも今、鮎原くんは…}But now, Ayuhara-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.84,Alternative,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{一ノ瀬、お前一体何を言いたいんだ。}Ichinose, what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:51.52,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{もう体育館をいらないと言いました。}…says she doesn't need the gym anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:55.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{このキャプテンの声で初めて 我が富士見学園バレー部は}I think that for the first time we heard from our Fujimi Academy's volleyball club's captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.51,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{専用の体育館を持つ資格を持ったんだと僕は思うんです。}…that her club is qualified to have its own gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.47,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{バレー部を浄水に愛するからこそ。}That's because her love for the club is pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{スポーツを愛するからこそ。}Same goes for her love for sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.15,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{今は何もいらないと時代した。}She doesn't need anything but those.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:10.58,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{そのバレー部のために 僕たちはなんとか 体育館建設を実現させて—}For this volleyball club, we should agree for the gym construction—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.95,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{そうだ！}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.67,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{一ノ瀬の言う通りだ。}It's just like Ichinose says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:17.25,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{我だが富士見学園の名を天下に轟くしてくれたバレー部に}It's a shame for us to say there's no place to practice…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:21.64,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{専用の練習場もないと言うこと 我々前向性との恥だ。}…to the team that roared our Fujimi Academy's title to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.35,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{そうだ！}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.85,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{いいぞ、三田村。}Nice, Mitamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.97,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ありがとう、努くん。三田村さん。}Thank you, Tsutomu-kun, Mitamura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:29.20,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{皆さん、どうですか？}What's your opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.85,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—賛成。—賛成。\N—XXあるかたはありませんか？}– Agreed!\N– Nobody opposes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:34.61,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{あ、では全員一で賛成と認めます。}Then it is an unanimous decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:38.77,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{よろしい。}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:46.37,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{ではバレー部専用体育館建設の件は 職員会議にかけたうえ 正式に決定します。}The final decision on the volleyball club's dedicated gym will be reviewed in the next staff meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:50.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{努くん、どうも有難う。}Tsutomu-kun, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:51.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それから三田村さんも。}Mitamura-san, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.51,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{うん。俺今日は一ノ瀬を見直したよ。}Today I saw Ichinose in a better light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.76,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{お前いいことを言うな。}You can say nice things once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:58.27,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{おい、握手しよう。}Let's shake on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:21:59.48,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{ん。しかし…}Yep. However…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:02.34,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{三田村と僕とはライバルとあることは変えないぜ。}It doesn't change that Mitamura and I are rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:06.27,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{ん？あ、あ。いいぞ。}Hm? Y-Yeah. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:07.71,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{ハハハハ。}Hahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:10.49,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{我々としては一応喜ぶべきことだが…}It means a great honor to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:13.58,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{…それだけに責任はますます重くなるわけだ。}But it also means heavier responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:16.44,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{え、差し当たり目前に迫っている全国大会だが…}We have the next All-Japan championship around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:20.90,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{今後の練習スケジュールは全て この大会に焦点を合わせることにする。}The upcoming practices schedule will focus on that tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:24.94,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{これからはほとんどのことを 鮎原にやってもらうことにするから。}From now on, I will have Ayuhara do most of the things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.94,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{皆もそのつもりでいってもらいたい。}I'd like you to go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:30.18,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{鮎原ならそれが出きるはずだ。}I'm sure Ayuhara will handle it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:33.17,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{諸君もキャプテンの言うこと 私の言うことだと思って。}Treat her orders as if they were mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:35.33,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{練習に励んでほしい。}I want you to work hard at the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:36.47,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{いいな？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.47,0:22:37.99,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{—はい！\N—はい！}– Yes sir!\N– Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:40.25,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{よし。それじゃ、今日はここで解散する。}All right. That's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:43.03,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{明日からのスケジュールはキャプテンが決めろ。}The captain will decide the schedule from tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.03,0:22:44.31,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{いいな、鮎原？}Got it, Ayuhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:44.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:47.21,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{では、解散。}Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:51.73,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{こずえ、お手やらかにね。}Kozue, take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:53.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{うん。みどり、助けてね。}Midori, you'll help me out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:56.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{私一人でとっても 心細くって。}I don't think I can do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:57.38,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{なに言ってるの？}Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.38,0:22:59.46,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{あなたなら十分やれるわよ。}You will do just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:04.13,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{そうよ。鮎原さんならさ、本郷先生と間違った楽しさで練習できるわ。}Exactly. Practicing with Ayuhara-san will be much more fun than with professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:05.59,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{とにかく、いいことよ。}At any rate, it's a great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:06.24,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{本当。}Darn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:09.21,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{本郷先生XXXじゃん。}Professor Hongou will be shocked with the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:13.97,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,{でもコーチをあなたに任せて 本号先生は何をする気かしら？}But what is professor planning to do, leaving coaching to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.97,0:23:16.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{きっと作戦に(XX・せんけん・せんげん)するつもりよ。}I'm sure he has his motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.82,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{又「作戦無き作戦」何てこと考え出すかもよ。}It reminds me of the "strategy without strategy".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:20.78,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:21.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい？}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:24.13,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{あ、あなたに手紙だよ。}There's a letter to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？あたしに？}Eh? Where from?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:26.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,{福岡中学内\N垣之内良子}Fukuoka Middle School\NKakinouchi Yoshiko
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:30.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ま、福岡中学の垣之内さんからだわ。}It's from Kakinouchi-san of Fukuoka's Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:31.44,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{へ？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:33.13,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{何であの人から？}What did she write?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:36.09,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ま。}My.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:37.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{挑戦状だわ。}It's a letter of challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.55,0:23:42.13,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうだ、シェレーニナ。}All right, Shellenina.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:46.03,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あなたと戦う前に、もう一人戦わなければならない人がいったわ。}There is someone else I need to fight before we battle each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.69,0:23:56.43,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{福岡中学垣之内良子自信に満ちた挑戦状。}Kakinouchi of Fukuoka Middle School delivers a perky challenge letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:24:01.55,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{こずえは本号コーチに誓う： 「こちらも新しい力で戦うのみだ」。}Kozue makes a promise to coach Hongou to fight with a new strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.55,0:24:06.03,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{こずえは夏休みの合宿 軽井沢でと言う みどりの提案もXXX。}Midori offers a plan to spend the summer vacation camping in Karuizawa. Kozue rejects it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.03,0:24:08.60,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{連日厳しくトレーニングを指導する。}She wants to hold strict training sessions every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.60,0:24:14.92,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{だが、そんなこずえにXX みどりやかしわぎ以下 部員の間に だんだん 反感が詰まっている。}The girls do not like the severity of the new training, including Kashiwagi and Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.92,0:24:17.32,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{そしてついにXXXは爆発した。}Finally, a rebellion explodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:21.08,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
